									</h2>
									<t t-if="len(o.workcenter_lines) > 0">
										<span style="margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px;" t-field="o.workcenter_lines[0].workcenter_id.name" />
									</t>
									
								</td>
								<td
									style="border-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; vertical-align: center;">
